creator: SOCAR GLOBAL
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the SOCAR V2 Beta App!

Please note that this is a test app, still in Beta.

For the full SOCAR experience, please use the current version of the SOCAR app.

You can install our SOCAR V2 Beta App alongside your current version of SOCAR app, to test out new features in early beta. Working features in SOCAR V2 Beta App include Sign Up, Booking, Unlocking and Driving.

We are open to your reviews and feedback. Let us know what you think and help make the next SOCAR V2 app the best car-sharing app in Malaysia!

About SOCAR
SOCAR is Malaysia’s No.1 Car-Sharing App. Book from over 2,000 cars in KL, Selangor, Penang, JB, Ipoh, and Negeri Sembilan, right from the SOCAR app, from as low as RM8/hour. Enjoy a wide variety of services - SOCAR-2-U, Oneway Intercity, Oneway Airport, and even personal driver service SOCAR+ with 24 Hour Live Customer Support Service.

#MoreThanJustACar
